It’s 2021 baby! New year, new stories, same old chaos. This week we’re joined with Clouter Banks star, Todd Eric Smith as we recap our holiday experiences together. Sit back, relax, and protect your mother’s at all costs...you never know what mortifying situations they can get themselves into. Possibly witnessing adults at play? Enjoy, and Happy New Year!
